    <title>Ubuntu配置java环境</title>
    <link href="http://hwang.tech/2022/08/19/Ubuntu%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEjava%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/"/>
    <id>http://hwang.tech/2022/08/19/Ubuntu%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEjava%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/</id>
    <published>2022-08-19T06:16:37.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-08-19T06:17:08.838Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Ubuntu配置Java"><a href="#Ubuntu配置Java" class="headerlink" title="Ubuntu配置Java"></a>Ubuntu配置Java</h2><h4 id="Java环境"><a href="#Java环境" class="headerlink" title="Java环境"></a>Java环境</h4><p>Java和JVM（Java的虚拟机）是许多软件所必需的，包括<a href="http://tomcat.apache.org/">Tomcat</a>，<a href="https://www.eclipse.org/jetty/">Jetty</a>，<a href="https://javaee.github.io/glassfish/">Glassfish</a>，<a href="http://cassandra.apache.org/">Cassandra</a>和<a href="https://jenkins.io/">Jenkins</a>。</p><h4 id="安装默认Java"><a href="#安装默认Java" class="headerlink" title="安装默认Java"></a>安装默认Java</h4><p>安装Java的最简单方法是使用与Ubuntu一起打包的版本。默认情况下，Ubuntu 18.04包含Open JDK，它是JRE和JDK的开源变体。</p><p>该软件包将安装OpenJDK 10或11。</p><ul><li>在2018年9月之前，这将安装OpenJDK 10。</li><li>2018年9月之后，这将安装OpenJDK 11。</li></ul><p>要安装此版本，请先更新本地软件包：</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo apt update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接下来，检查是否已安装Java：</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ java -version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果当前未安装Java，您将看到以下输出：</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title class_">Command</span> <span class="string">&#x27;java&#x27;</span> not found</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>执行以下命令安装OpenJDK：</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo apt install <span class="keyword">default</span>-jre</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此命令将安装Java运行时环境（JRE）。这将允许您运行几乎所有Java软件。</p><p>验证安装：</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ java -version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>您将看到以下输出：</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">openjdk version <span class="string">&quot;10.0.1&quot;</span> <span class="number">2018</span>-<span class="number">04</span>-<span class="number">17</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title class_">OpenJDK</span> <span class="title class_">Runtime</span> <span class="title class_">Environment</span> (build <span class="number">10.0</span><span class="number">.1</span>+<span class="number">10</span>-<span class="title class_">Ubuntu</span>-3ubuntu1)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="title class_">OpenJDK</span> <span class="number">64</span>-<span class="title class_">Bit</span> <span class="title class_">Server</span> <span class="variable constant_">VM</span> (build <span class="number">10.0</span><span class="number">.1</span>+<span class="number">10</span>-<span class="title class_">Ubuntu</span>-3ubuntu1, mixed mode)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>除了JRE之外，您可能还需要Java Development Kit（JDK）才能编译和运行某些特定的基于Java的软件。要安装JDK，请执行以下命令，该命令还将安装JRE：</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo apt install <span class="keyword">default</span>-jdk</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>通过检查Java编译器的<code>javac</code>版本，来验证是否已安装JDK ：</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ javac -version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>您将看到以下输出：</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">11.0</span><span class="number">.16</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="手动安装"><a href="#手动安装" class="headerlink" title="手动安装"></a>手动安装</h4><p>从网上找一个jdk的tar.gz包，上传到Ubuntu</p><p>解压安装包到指定位置</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar –xvf jdk-xxx.tar.gz –C /home/anyone/resources # 位置看个人习惯</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改配置环境</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 打开文件</span><br><span class="line">sudo vim /etc/profile</span><br><span class="line"># 设置环境变量</span><br><span class="line"># 拷贝下列配置代码进入</span><br><span class="line"> JAVA_HOME= jdk解压的文件夹的绝对路径 # 上述路径</span><br><span class="line"> CLASSPATH=.:$JAVA_HOME/lib.tools.jar</span><br><span class="line"> PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin:$PATH</span><br><span class="line"> export JAVA_HOME CLASSPATH PATH</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重新加载<code>/etc/profile</code>配置文件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo source /etc/profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看java版本</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">java -version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
